  "detailed_description": "<strong>Froggy's battle is a cute and loopy take on the action roguelike genre</strong>. Master <strong>unique loop movement</strong>, build your dream frog with <strong>shiny upgrades</strong>, and you might be able to survive the ongoing <strong>waves of angry enemies and strong bosses</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/571dc63565531e7520427ed52efdb29d.poster.avif?t=1759917430\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/571dc63565531e7520427ed52efdb29d.webm?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/571dc63565531e7520427ed52efdb29d.mp4?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skate that loop!</h2>Tired of moving by simply walking? Good news, that frog doesn't even know how to walk, but she sure as heck can <strong>skate</strong>!  <br>Ride along the <strong>loop</strong> arena, turn around, jump, crouch, accelerate, do whatever you need to evade enemies attacks and give them a taste of your weapons!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/6f98b6631bf3333f9327fac81efde4bf.poster.avif?t=1759917430\" width=640 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/6f98b6631bf3333f9327fac81efde4bf.webm?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/6f98b6631bf3333f9327fac81efde4bf.mp4?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose cool upgrades!</h2>A simple ollie is cool and all, but how about doing a kickflip that's so fast that it summons thunder while swinging a huge sword and throwing fireballs? You could do that, or a backflip while blasting loud music and launching a bowling ball, that's up to you to decide!  <br>Choose your <strong>weapons</strong>, change your skateboard <strong>tricks</strong>, upgrade your <strong>stats </strong>and become unstoppable!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/842babd1d5dce395a95827d330fe5695.poster.avif?t=1759917430\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/842babd1d5dce395a95827d330fe5695.webm?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/842babd1d5dce395a95827d330fe5695.mp4?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive waves of cute enemies!</h2>You thought you could skate peacefully today, but that<strong> frog army</strong> won't let you. They'll come bouncing, flying, rolling, and they'll even send their big <strong>bosses</strong>.  <br>Do anything you can to keep them away, and be warned: they might be cute, but they sure are angry and <strong>many</strong>!<br><br><br><i>Trailer music by Heatley Bros</i>",
