ll, but how about doing a kickflip that's so fast that it summons thunder while swinging a huge sword and throwing fireballs? You could do that, or a backflip while blasting loud music and launching a bowling ball, that's up to you to decide!  <br>Choose your <strong>weapons</strong>, change your skateboard <strong>tricks</strong>, upgrade your <strong>stats </strong>and become unstoppable!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/842babd1d5dce395a95827d330fe5695.poster.avif?t=1759917430\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/842babd1d5dce395a95827d330fe5695.webm?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424650/extras/842babd1d5dce395a95827d330fe5695.mp4?t=1759917430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive waves of cute enemies!</h2>You thought you could skate peacefully today, but that<strong> frog army</strong> won't let you. They'll come bouncing, flying, rolling, and they'll even send their big <strong>bosses</strong>.  <br>Do anything you can to keep them away, and be warned: they might be cute, but they sure are angry and <strong>many</strong>!<br><br><br><i>Trailer music by Heatley Bros</i>",
